{"id":"807380837282758656","type":"text","timestamp":1769978368,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/807380837282758656","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/807093590137421824\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p>I’m high on existence. </p><p>Our anxiety and fear’s aren’t gone… but crying about them for a few days helped a lot.</p><p>We are… not good… but better.</p><p>And I still love being me.</p><p>- Lark</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"807093590137421824"}}],"baseline_notes":33,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}